sql: SELECT AVG(u.order_id), u.order_status_code, u.customer_id FROM Customer_Orders AS u WHERE  u.customer_id < 12 GROUP BY u.customer_id HAVING AVG(u.order_id) > 46 LIMIT 9
SELECT job_title_code, department_name FROM Staff_Department_Assignments JOIN Departments ON Departments.department_id = Staff_Department_Assignments.department_id ORDER BY department_name ASC

SELECT Staff.staff_id, staff_name FROM Staff_Department_Assignments JOIN Staff ON Staff_Department_Assignments.staff_id = Staff.staff_id WHERE Staff.staff_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND EXISTS (SELECT * FROM Staff_Department_Assignments AS v WHERE  v.staff_id = Staff.staff_id AND v.department_id >= 27) GROUP BY Staff.staff_name ORDER BY Staff.staff_id DESC
SELECT COUNT(department_id), department_id FROM Departments GROUP BY department_id ORDER BY department_id DESC LIMIT 5
SELECT supplier_name, supplier_phone FROM Suppliers WHERE supplier_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 GROUP BY supplier_name ORDER BY supplier_name DESC

SELECT COUNT(product_id), MAX(supplier_id), date_supplied_from FROM Product_Suppliers WHERE product_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND total_value_purchased NOT IN (SELECT total_value_purchased FROM Product_Suppliers) GROUP BY date_supplied_from
SELECT MAX(w.dept_store_id), w.department_name FROM Departments AS w WHERE  w.department_id < 19 GROUP BY w.department_name HAVING COUNT(w.department_id) < 14 ORDER BY w.department_name ASC

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT y.date_assigned_from), y.staff_id, y.job_title_code FROM Staff_Department_Assignments AS y WHERE date_assigned_from > (SELECT MIN(date_assigned_from) FROM Staff_Department_Assignments AS l WHERE l.staff_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10) ORDER BY y.staff_id ASC LIMIT 9
SELECT staff_id, staff_name FROM Staff WHERE  staff_id >= 54 ORDER BY staff_name ASC LIMIT 1

SELECT SUM(Product_Suppliers.product_id), Order_Items.order_id, Product_Suppliers.supplier_id FROM Product_Suppliers JOIN Products ON Product_Suppliers.product_id = Products.product_id JOIN Suppliers ON Suppliers.supplier_id = Product_Suppliers.supplier_id JOIN Order_Items ON Order_Items.product_id = Products.product_id WHERE Products.product_price BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR Order_Items.product_id > 31 GROUP BY Product_Suppliers.supplier_id

SELECT MIN(Department_Store_Chain.dept_store_chain_id), AVG(Department_Stores.dept_store_id), COUNT(DISTINCT Department_Stores.dept_store_id), Department_Store_Chain.dept_store_chain_name FROM Department_Stores JOIN Department_Store_Chain ON Department_Stores.dept_store_chain_id = Department_Store_Chain.dept_store_chain_id WHERE Department_Stores.dept_store_chain_id = 73 GROUP BY Department_Store_Chain.dept_store_chain_name
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT n.dept_store_chain_id), n.store_email FROM Department_Stores AS n GROUP BY n.store_email;
SELECT staff_id FROM Staff WHERE  staff_id < 61 LIMIT 1

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT c.supplier_phone), c.supplier_phone FROM Suppliers AS c WHERE c.supplier_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR supplier_name NOT IN (SELECT supplier_name FROM Suppliers WHERE  supplier_id < 8 LIMIT 7)
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT u.order_item_id), u.order_id FROM Order_Items AS u WHERE u.product_id BETWEEN 1 AND 18 LIMIT 9

SELECT MAX(customer_id), customer_id, customer_email FROM Customers WHERE customer_id = 80 OR EXISTS (SELECT * FROM Customer_Addresses WHERE Customers.customer_id = Customer_Addresses.customer_id) ORDER BY customer_id DESC;
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT department_name) FROM Departments WHERE department_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10;

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT dept_store_chain_name), Department_Stores.dept_store_chain_id FROM Department_Stores JOIN Department_Store_Chain ON Department_Stores.dept_store_chain_id = Department_Store_Chain.dept_store_chain_id ORDER BY Department_Stores.dept_store_chain_id ASC
SELECT payment_method_code FROM Customer_Addresses JOIN Customers ON Customer_Addresses.customer_id = Customers.customer_id WHERE Customer_Addresses.customer_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10
SELECT order_status_code FROM Customer_Orders JOIN Order_Items ON Customer_Orders.order_id = Order_Items.order_id WHERE  product_id >= 37 ORDER BY order_status_code DESC
SELECT AVG(order_id), product_id FROM Order_Items WHERE order_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 GROUP BY product_id ORDER BY product_id DESC LIMIT 10
SELECT b.dept_store_id, b.store_phone FROM Department_Stores AS b WHERE  b.dept_store_id > 19 GROUP BY b.dept_store_id

SELECT MIN(Products.product_id), Products.product_name FROM Product_Suppliers INNER JOIN Products ON Product_Suppliers.product_id = Products.product_id INNER JOIN Order_Items ON Products.product_id = Order_Items.product_id GROUP BY Products.product_name LIMIT 6
SELECT w.supplier_id FROM Product_Suppliers AS w
SELECT product_type_code FROM Products JOIN Order_Items ON Order_Items.product_id = Products.product_id
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT staff_gender), COUNT(DISTINCT staff_id), staff_id, staff_name FROM Staff WHERE staff_id >= 69 GROUP BY staff_name, staff_id ORDER BY staff_name DESC
SELECT customer_id, customer_name FROM Customers WHERE customer_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 ORDER BY customer_name ASC

SELECT supplier_phone, supplier_name FROM Suppliers JOIN Supplier_Addresses ON Supplier_Addresses.supplier_id = Suppliers.supplier_id WHERE Supplier_Addresses.supplier_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 GROUP BY supplier_name LIMIT 7

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT product_price), product_name, date_supplied_to FROM Product_Suppliers JOIN Products ON Products.product_id = Product_Suppliers.product_id WHERE  Products.product_id >= 84 AND product_price > (SELECT AVG(product_price) FROM Products WHERE  product_id != 79) GROUP BY date_supplied_to ORDER BY product_name ASC LIMIT 5
SELECT AVG(supplier_id), supplier_phone FROM Suppliers WHERE supplier_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 LIMIT 8
SELECT address_id FROM Customer_Addresses WHERE customer_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR  address_id >= 88 LIMIT 3
